"12  small rainbow carrots, preferably with tops, scrubbed","3  small heads fennel, ends and tough outer leaves trimmed","2  bunches baby turnips (about 12) or 6 medium regular turnips","2  or 3 bunches small red radishes with leaves","2  scarlet turnips or 1 watermelon radish (optional), thinly sliced crosswise","  Olio nuovo or other extra-virgin olive oil"